				{
					name = {"奈々瀬", "Nanase"},
					"“Not just that. The 'long rope' one that Hinami mentioned is a competition to see how many pulls it takes before they ejaculate. The pairs one is probably the erect long jump, where they compete to see whose semen flies the farthest.”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
