					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					name = {"美岬", "Misaki"},
					"“I was, before. I thought I could lose weight just through exercise, so I was doing a lot of masturba... sorry... uh, how do I put this...? Sexual solitaire...?”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					name = {"美岬"},
					"“嗯……根本不行。在运动减肥的信念下，我用手……对不起……那个……该怎么说才好呢……性方面的运动……？”",
